<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA65">
<l>kālaiyē pōṉṟilaṅku mēṉi kaṭumpakaliṉ</l>
<l>vēlaiyē pōṉṟilaṅkum veṇṇīṟu - mālaiyiṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṅkuruvē pōluñ caṭaikkaṟṟai maṟṟavaṟku</l>
<l>vīṅkiruḷē pōlu miṭaṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the morning shines the body. Like the time</l>
<l>of fierce midday shine the white ashes. The lasting  form</l>
<l>of evening [red] resembles the bundle of matted hair. Then again, his</l>
<l>throat resembles swelling darkness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
